      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>meat-free hot dog sausage[s]</strong> to one side of a baking tray (use<strong> tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 20 min</p>",
