    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>macaroni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 7 min or until it's cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>macaroni</strong>, reserving the pot</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1695196410220-x200.jpg",
