        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 6-8 min or until golden, stirring frequently – these are your <strong>garlic breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695196416230-x200.jpg",
