          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and stir for 1-2 min or until a sandy paste forms – this is your <strong>roux</strong></p><p>Gradually add 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> into the <strong>roux </strong>with your <strong>soft cheese </strong>and whisk for 3-4 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1695196420956-x200.jpg",
