    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>tomato wedges </strong>and <strong>quick-pickled shallot </strong>to a bowl with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato & shallot</strong> <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Cut a slit into the top of the <strong>warmed hot dog bun[s]</strong></p>",
